gle, 即係大陸牌子未來都要另外起條hk 版先有機會有felica chip.  大陸封鎖google, 未來要有大陸an 機有felica 又supoort google pay 既機會好難.<br />\n<br />\nsony 新到xz3 , 唔係日版既都無felica. 其他牌子an 機就更加無<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://rezv.net/android/36586/#Xperia_XZ3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frezv.net%2Fandroid%2F36586%2F%23Xperia_XZ3&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852wogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=5e5dfe5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://rezv.net/android/36586/#Xperia_XZ3</a><br />\n<br />\n我諗要八仔support an 機睇黎唔易"},{"pid":"fdf2e547c6ff4341066fc4e6f3dec02dc6cdf3ad","tid":1306703,"uid":57424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f199f9f08f607da008fb4f7fd57e3ae7cdec7b62","tid":1306703,"uid":1826,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/12/13/everything-about-smart-octopus-qa/tips-2/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2Feverything-about-smart-octopus-qa%2Ftips-2%2Famp%2F&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852wogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=710b014d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/12/13/everything-about-smart-octopus-qa/tips-2/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n查左下, an 機要support 到八達通, 又如果八達通support  google pay 的話, 部an 機要有Felica chip. 跟據上面條link 所講, an 機就算samsung 本身都要s8 以上先有. 其他an 機無. <br />\n<br />\n大陸封鎖google, 即係大陸牌子未來都要另外起條hk 版先有機會有felica chip.  大陸封鎖google, 未來要有大陸an 機有felica 又supoort google pay 既機會好難.<br />\n<br />\nsony 新到xz3 , 唔係日版既都無felica. 其他牌子an 機就更加無<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://rezv.net/android/36586/#Xperia_XZ3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frezv.net%2Fandroid%2F36586%2F%23Xperia_XZ3&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852wogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=5e5dfe5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://rezv.net/android/36586/#Xperia_XZ3</a><br />\n<br />\n我諗要八仔support an 機睇黎唔易"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:49:34.000Z","msg":"屌呀，姐係無希望<br />\n最新既 xperia 1 查一查都係要日版先有"},{"pid":"f94768467e819c2b882b0f92e7d2baed1c5b09c4","tid":1306703,"uid":34161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f199f9f08f607da008fb4f7fd57e3ae7cdec7b62","tid":1306703,"uid":1826,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:28:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/12/13/everything-about-smart-octopus-qa/tips-2/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2Feverything-about-smart-octopus-qa%2Ftips-2%2Famp%2F&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852wogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=710b014d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/12/13/everything-about-smart-octopus-qa/tips-2/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n查左下, an 機要support 到八達通, 又如果八達通support  google pay 的話, 部an 機要有Felica chip. 跟據上面條link 所講, an 機就算samsung 本身都要s8 以上先有. 其他an 機無. <br />\n<br />\n大陸封鎖google, 即係大陸牌子未來都要另外起條hk 版先有機會有felica chip.  大陸封鎖google, 未來要有大陸an 機有felica 又supoort google pay 既機會好難.<br />\n<br />\nsony 新到xz3 , 唔係日版既都無felica. 其他牌子an 機就更加無<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://rezv.net/android/36586/#Xperia_XZ3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frezv.net%2Fandroid%2F36586%2F%23Xperia_XZ3&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852wogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=5e5dfe5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://rezv.net/android/36586/#Xperia_XZ3</a><br />\n<br />\n我諗要八仔support an 機睇黎唔易"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T13:51:49.000Z","msg":"以我嘅理解，要用到八達通嘅條件係:<br />\n1. 要有 NFC secure element (SIM 或內置)<br />\n2. secure element 要有八達通 application (唔係 Osaifu-Keitai 嗰隻 FeliCa application)<br />\n3. 部機嘅 OS 要有 API 讀寫到 secure element<br />\n4. 要有個支援到八達通嘅 app<br />\n<br />\n我唔清楚 samsung pay 八達通係點運作 (我指商業上)，不過八達通 app 嗰邊睇落只係直接 call 返 samsung pay 嘅 library，即係 samsung pay 支援八達通嘅 code 都喺晒 samsung 嗰邊，應該唔可以輕易 apply 到其他 Android 機 (不過都有可能啲 code 係八達通自己寫完授權俾 samsung 用)<br />\n<br />\n如果要整個全部 android 機通用嘅 embedded secure element 加埋有八達通 application 應該好難，最多真係特登出港版機咁樣<br />\n<br />\n感覺上現時最可行都係用 SIM 咭<br />\n一係就八達通轉用 HCE (但係咁有好多技術問題)"},{"pid":"d875298f8fc25dd1fa270b14dc951383dc739582","tid":1306703,"uid":107898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"203ba4b017cdef8